onChange.script:
analysis_setting = system.mes.analysis.createMESAnalysisSettings("quality_setting_general")
	datapoints = [
				"Hour Interval",
				"OEE Outfeed Count",
				"OEE Reject Count",
				"OEE Quality"
				]
	analysis_setting.setDataPoints(datapoints)
	analysis_setting.addParameter('eqPath')
	analysis_setting.setFilterExpression("Equipment Path = @eqPath")
	#analysis_setting.setGroupBy("Hour Interval")
	 
	start_date = system.date.parse(self.view.params.startDate,'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss')
	end_date = system.date.parse(self.view.params.endDate,'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss')
	params = {'eqPath':self.view.params.eqPath}
	data =  system.mes.analysis.executeAnalysis(start_date, end_date, analysis_setting, params).getDataset()
	pyData = system.dataset.toPyDataSet(data)
	if len(pyData)>0:
		self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("CoordinateContainer").getChild("FlexContainer_production").getChild("Label_production").props.text = pyData[0]['OEE Outfeed Count']
		self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("CoordinateContainer").getChild("FlexContainer_waste").getChild("Label_waste").props.text = pyData[0]['OEE Reject Count']
		self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("CoordinateContainer").getChild("SimpleGauge").props.value = int(pyData[0]['OEE Quality']*100)
	else:
		self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("CoordinateContainer").getChild("FlexContainer_production").getChild("Label_production").props.text = 0
		self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("CoordinateContainer").getChild("FlexContainer_waste").getChild("Label_waste").props.text = 0
		self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("CoordinateContainer").getChild("SimpleGauge").props.value = 0
	system.perspective.sendMessage('refresh')

messageHandlers.script:
# implement your handler here
	analysis_setting = system.mes.analysis.createMESAnalysisSettings("quality_setting")
	datapoints = [
				"Hour Interval",
				"OEE Outfeed Count",
				"OEE Reject Count",
				"OEE Quality"
				]
	analysis_setting.setDataPoints(datapoints)
	analysis_setting.addParameter('eqPath')
	analysis_setting.setFilterExpression("Equipment Path = @eqPath")
	analysis_setting.setGroupBy("Hour Interval")
	 
	start_date = system.date.parse(self.view.params.startDate,'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss')
	end_date = system.date.parse(self.view.params.endDate,'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss')
	params = {'eqPath':self.view.params.eqPath}
	data =  system.mes.analysis.executeAnalysis(start_date, end_date, analysis_setting, params).getDataset()
	pyData = system.dataset.toPyDataSet(data)
	dic = []
	for row in pyData:
		temp = {'Hour': row['Hour Interval'],u'Production':row['OEE Outfeed Count'],'Waste':row['OEE Reject Count'],'Quality':(row['OEE Quality'])*100}
		dic.append(temp)
	self.props.dataSources.Quality = dic
	self.getSibling("Table").props.data = dic
